{"id":434122,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/04/vox｜一组漫画看懂巴拿马文件泄露事件/","date":"2016-04-05T06:36:41Z","modified":"2016-04-05T06:40:25Z","title":"Vox｜一组漫画看懂巴拿马文件泄露事件","content":"<p>【编者注】本文由中国数字时代编辑翻译自 <em>Vox </em>文章<em> <a href=\"http://www.vox.com/2016/4/4/11361780/the-panama-papers-cartoon\" target=\"_blank\">The Panama Papers leak, explained with an adorable comic about piggy banks</a></em>；请点击原文链接阅读完整报道。</p>\n<p><strong>假设说你把自己的零钱存在衣柜架上的储蓄罐里。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank01.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434134\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434134\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank01.png\" alt=\"piggybank01\" width=\"550\" height=\"327\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank01.png 800w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank01-300x178.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank01-768x456.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank01-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>但你妈妈总是动不动就来检查存取情况。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>你很不爽。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank02.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434133\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434133\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank02.png\" alt=\"piggybank02\" width=\"550\" height=\"330\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank02.png 794w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank02-300x180.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank02-768x461.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank02-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>然后你准备了另一个储蓄罐&#8230;</strong></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank03.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434132\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434132\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank03.png\" alt=\"piggybank03\" width=\"550\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank03.png 825w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank03-300x160.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank03-768x409.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>&#8230;带到强尼家。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank04.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434131\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434131\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank04.png\" alt=\"piggybank04\" width=\"550\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank04.png 847w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank04-300x166.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank04-768x426.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>强尼妈妈很忙，没空来检查。所以你能够把储蓄罐秘密地藏在那里，没人会来过问。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank05.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434130\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434130\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank05.png\" alt=\"piggybank05\" width=\"550\" height=\"305\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank05.png 847w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank05-300x166.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank05-768x426.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>小区里的其他小朋友都觉得这个主意很棒。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank06.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434129\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434129\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank06.png\" alt=\"piggybank06\" width=\"550\" height=\"288\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank06.png 858w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank06-300x157.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank06-768x402.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>所以他们也都把自己的储蓄罐藏到了强尼的衣柜里。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434128\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank07.png\" alt=\"piggybank07\" width=\"550\" height=\"169\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank07.png 858w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank07-300x92.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank07-768x235.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></strong></p>\n<p><strong>但有一天，强尼妈妈发现了这些储蓄罐。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank08.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434127\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434127\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank08.png\" alt=\"piggybank08\" width=\"550\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank08.png 873w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank08-300x192.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank08-768x491.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>她很生气，打电话给所有小朋友的家长，告诉他们这些孩子背着家长偷偷藏钱。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank09.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434126\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434126\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank09.png\" alt=\"piggybank09\" width=\"550\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank09.png 786w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank09-300x164.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank09-768x419.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>今天的文件泄露事件基本就是这么回事。很多重要的、有权势的人物都把自己的储蓄罐藏在了强尼在巴拿马的家。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank10.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434125\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434125\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank10.png\" alt=\"piggybank10\" width=\"550\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank10.png 795w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank10-300x181.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank10-768x464.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank10-80x48.png 80w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>当然，不是每个藏钱的人都是因为做了坏事。比如，你只是不想你妈妈侵犯你的隐私。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>但你的邻居迈克尔是把从他妈妈包里偷来的钱藏在强尼的衣柜里。雅各布则是因为偷了其他小朋友的零花钱，不想被家长问他这些钱是哪儿来的。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>我们很快就会知道谁在做坏事，谁是清白的。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank11.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434124\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434124\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank11.png\" alt=\"piggybank11\" width=\"550\" height=\"162\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank11.png 786w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank11-300x88.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank11-768x226.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>但每个在强尼家藏钱的人还是都惹了麻烦，因为秘密储蓄罐是不被允许的。</strong></p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank12.png\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-434123\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-434123\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank12.png\" alt=\"piggybank12\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank12.png 786w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank12-300x225.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/04/piggybank12-768x576.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></strong></p>\n<p><strong>所以记者们正在整理这些文件，想要搞清在强尼巴拿马的家里到底发生了什么性质的活动——是合法的、合理的、还是违法的。Vox 巴拿马文件专题报道<a href=\"http://www.vox.com/2016/4/4/11361436/panama-papers-list-leaks-fonseca-names-politicians\" target=\"_blank\">点此</a>。</strong></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,20534],"tags":[13232,30715,24543,14693,29669]}